data.description: Lovely single-story with a stunning pool, in the master-planned community of Tuscan Lakes! This home offers fresh paint in the living room/kitchen/secondary bedrooms, a new water heater (Jan 2023), a private front porch, nice vinyl plank and tile flooring throughout, a study/flex room with new carpet, and a spacious living area great for entertaining! The kitchen includes a breakfast bar island, granite countertops, tile backsplash, stainless steel appliances, recessed lighting, French doors to the backyard, and ample cabinet space while the master bedroom features a remodeled walk-in closet and jetted tub! Both secondary bedrooms also have new carpet! Enjoy outdoor entertaining with both open and covered patio spaces, a pool, the upgraded deck area, and no back neighbor for added privacy! Located with proximity to I-45, Kemah, and Galveston!
